trans-unit.source: Argument 'number' cannot convert from TypeA to TypeB

trans-unit.source: The type of one argument in a method does not match the type that was passed when the class was instantiated.
trans-unit.target: O tipo de um argumento em um método não coincide com o tipo passado quando a classe foi instanciada.

trans-unit.source: This error typically appears along with CS1502.
trans-unit.target: Este erro geralmente aparece junto com CS1502.

trans-unit.source: See [CS1502](../../csharp/language-reference/compiler-messages/cs1502.md) for a discussion of how to resolve this error.
